original_title: Shane's World 29: Frat Row Scavenger Hunt 3
overview: This installment of Shane's World is what started the spark. Watch the crew go to ASU and partake in a nasty Scavenger Hunt. You may have seen reports on MTV, or CNN. Mainstream press picked up this story and the backlash has spun this title into a huge industry hit. See what all the fuss is about as Calli Cox, Bobbi Barrington and the rest of the gang get those college boys to do so many nasty things!
title: Shane's World 29: Frat Row Scavenger Hunt 3
